metadata.name: Quintelarium: Dolls - #1 Zordelia
metadata.description:
“Virtual world or your world? Maybe there’s no difference...”
- Zordelia Quintel

Quintelarium is a series of NFTs that visually explores the concept of being inside of the other side of the screen. The Dolls are a subpart of the Quintelarium universe, personas living in a virtual world.

1080 x 1920 px | 25fps | MP4
Created by Miguel Baptista
